  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of ISIS-GCGRRx in Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Phase 2 Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of ISIS 449884 Administered Once Weekly to Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Being Treated With Metformin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
